{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the &quot;<strong>Christmas Store: Santa's Supermarket Simulator</strong>&quot;, you will have to manage the holiday store and make it the perfect place to shop for New Year gifts. Fill the shelves with seasonal goods such as Christmas decorations, presents, and other winter holiday items. Decide which products to stock, set prices, and run promotions to attract customers before the holidays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/Preview.gif?t=1739493318\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What to do?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your main task is to manage your resources and staff competently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/Buying.gif?t=1739493318\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hire employees to help with checkout, display goods, and keep the store tidy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/PlacingGoods.gif?t=1739493318\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decorate your store to create a winter wonderland atmosphere that will draw in customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/StoreDecoration.gif?t=1739493318\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your store by opening new sales areas and improving infrastructure to accommodate more customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3399990/extras/Expand.gif?t=1739493318\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph